data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your Florida haven in Riverside Park, Punta Gorda!  This custom-designed Florida-style home, nestled on over half an acre, offers a captivating blend of nature and luxury living.  Set among 22 majestic oak trees enveloped in Spanish moss, it boasts an open, meticulously maintained yard and a secluded backyard—a private sanctuary.  Step onto the full-width country-style front porch, an idyllic spot to immerse in nature's beauty.  The expansive lanai presents serene views of natural woods, a calming escape just 8 minutes from downtown Punta Gorda's vibrant activities.  Inside, discover a perfect blend of elegance and functionality.  Hardwood flooring graces the living room, kitchen, and dining area, fostering an inviting ambiance.  Indulge in the kitchen's stone counters, custom Craft made cabinetry, and stainless-steel appliances, making meal preparation a delightful experience.  Retreat to the spacious owner's suite featuring a tray ceiling and a luxurious river pebble mosaic floored shower in the ensuite bathroom—a private retreat to unwind after a long day.  The split-bedroom layout ensures ample space and comfort for family and guests alike.  Embrace the potential offered by the additional unfinished concrete block structure, which presents endless possibilities—a perfect space for storage, a craft room, a workshop, or a potential tiny house.  Complementing this space is a sizable storage shed equipped with 20-amp hookups—flexibility and convenience at your fingertips.   An extremely accommodating driveway provides ample space for multiple vehicles or an RV.  Rest easy knowing this home was constructed above hurricane standards, featuring impact glass and strapping-in walls every 36 inches, providing exceptional strength and security against the elements.   The community offers a convenient boat ramp to Shell Creek and Peace River, beckoning outdoor enthusiasts to embrace kayaking, fishing, and boating adventures in this picturesque locale. The expansive driveway ensures ample parking for multiple vehicles or an RV.  The laundry room doubling as a secure space adds to the convenience and functionality of this remarkable home.  Riverside Park embodies the quintessential Florida lifestyle—a harmonious blend of natural beauty, modern comforts, and endless opportunities for relaxation and recreation.  Don't miss your chance to make this your dream home!  Schedule your visit today and step into the Florida living you've always envisioned.
